{
  "voice_id": "7kXNOCqiaLdszL0OEXks",
  "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
  "voice_settings": {
    "stability": 0.65,
    "similarity_boost": 0.65,
    "style": 0.0,
    "speed": 1.13,
    "use_speaker_boost": true
  },
  "pronunciation_dictionary_locators": [
    {
      "pronunciation_dictionary_id": "AhK3J8mZDRoShxfoJLk6",
      "version_id": "pFvyQBbxEBKyF7C3IHpy"
    }
  ],
  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Anthropic's CEO said something in March 2025 that made every developer stop scrolling.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5dde62afa858d5abee96c52b87a4a25cfabde901017b6e042ef394800d24160a",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 5.433469387755102,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "At the Council on Foreign Relations, Dario Amodei said this: \"I think we will be there in three to six months \u2014 where AI is writing ninety percent of the code.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9c1f8769406982987fcc040627a0f0063c15471dbf4543a24a595165819f9a80",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 9.195102040816327,
      "word_count": 31,
      "words_offset": 13
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "And then in twelve months, we may be in a world where AI is writing essentially all of the code.\"\n\nNot someday.",
      "checksum": "sha256:99cef2141e63af3074b0058a8fb5dc3804b3cfa059e6797f0ab4237e380d6d1c",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 6.826666666666667,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 44
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Not eventually. Twelve months. And here's what most people missed: he also said his own engineers at Anthropic already say \u2014 quote \u2014 \"I don't write any code anymore.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f8141f7dc2b2aa91141f26f4437f38927e822cfe8451dea4d8140d4e76467bf2",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 11.145578231292516,
      "word_count": 29,
      "words_offset": 66
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "I let the model write the code, I just edit it.\"\n\nSo is this the end for developers?",
      "checksum": "sha256:34015556bbb59a669c219bb924dcfc502d741d37c615f22eaa479bcb47cbdf39",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 4.504671201814059,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 95
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "Or is it something else entirely? Here's what he actually meant.",
      "checksum": "sha256:00b35b67029ff6c167d8d007dae061dcceecd16e043d60f44f14623081faf335",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 3.8080725623582765,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 113
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Amodei wasn't saying engineers disappear.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d088512a6e67c7d43d9ff6e1ccb16f333b1f7002bf61c869439bfb9aa7dd2a59",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 2.136235827664399,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 124
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "He was saying the thing that changes is what engineers spend their time on.",
      "checksum": "sha256:740f4d5b4d216fb64762228afd3a3fcbcdcfe18ba594086b05e17c0f5723e7e1",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 4.690430839002268,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 129
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "The programmer still needs to specify what the conditions are, what the overall app you're building looks like, what the architecture decisions are.",
      "checksum": "sha256:946f7bde1614ed3607663155e08c577a1794d7af6a79d2c06993e237549653e7",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 7.894784580498866,
      "word_count": 23,
      "words_offset": 143
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "The code gets written. The direction still comes from you.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6c59fe9e81d902c23be3cd18aa7951b79c3c4522f6818d0eaf7c70b757cc3ba1",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 166
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Think of it this way. A century ago, most writers spent hours on mechanical typewriters, retyping drafts.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1b43bb63b87ced8eb8b26b5465b813032ea50adb2a886a0c96437618c5ad1a32",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 7.151746031746032,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 176
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Today, writers still exist \u2014 they just don't spend their time on mechanical tasks.",
      "checksum": "sha256:58db3b0544fa30f4fd7f772034cb2bf536850e7298ece3333a95c645f6fc5665",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 4.829750566893424,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 193
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "The craft shifted up a level. That's what Amodei is describing.",
      "checksum": "sha256:165efbe5baa7ba21437d6876b62741a49622e5f12874fb219607eea8d6b4235d",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 207
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "But the timeline was wrong. We're now past the six-month mark on that prediction.",
      "checksum": "sha256:be4d94b29b40c16aa2b4c9e40b4587191cde2173d6d82b284cc94ca1321252c9",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 4.31891156462585,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 218
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "AI tools are everywhere \u2014 eighty-four percent of developers use them \u2014 but we are not in a world where AI writes ninety percent of code.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5f1d1c6af2f7b466017500932985f129e16d35f6b2f38cb2fe7310d39b0741ec",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 8.359183673469389,
      "word_count": 26,
      "words_offset": 232
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "The prediction was real, but the pace was off.",
      "checksum": "sha256:46d90f18e19503c6926c1aef81961f8024d67a9ad1adc470f2b510decda1e54b",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 2.5541950113378684,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 258
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "So what should you actually do right now?",
      "checksum": "sha256:11e849a6b210851802a529ec5092f68d6b63e2df1434bd9c3732b2b8dc97fbd0",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 2.136235827664399,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 267
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "First: stop writing code you don't need to write.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fb80ad53354464029a86db06a36041583d3969016226b6e9dffbedeae6d0f095",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 275
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "Claude Code, Cursor, Copilot \u2014 use them.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b24a7cbd68c4a9cf815fe574e5012d4b485ddfe6e71a62dcd136962a0d6d49d8",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 2.507755102040816,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 284
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "Engineers who use AI tools are shipping faster, not being replaced. The skill isn't coding anymore.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4bd5327d917e7060d8454e10b2c19c4d4553b316293891bae09b69585586c2fd",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 5.944308390022676,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 291
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "It's orchestrating. Second: go deeper on systems thinking.",
      "checksum": "sha256:08ec2cf1df2393bcb1ac3de9af004896cb69281ce4fa4037a25e0e6c8847cc55",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 3.900952380952381,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 307
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "The engineers who will matter most are the ones who understand architecture, who can break a problem into pieces, evaluate what the agent built, and catch when it goes wrong.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9bd48e92e8b8b7ab08fa04360d12fb37044b8b50c19c93ee94de9c0982739847",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 9.891700680272109,
      "word_count": 30,
      "words_offset": 315
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "That's not a skill AI replaces. That's the skill AI amplifies.",
      "checksum": "sha256:796e2efecde2721a04203936470e640d2e12e1293ec900e0071d3aa40ce1636d",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 3.8080725623582765,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 345
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "Third: stop ignoring this. The companies not adapting now will be the ones scrambling in two years.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b24275894fabf35bb860ea1c21e928b16612a91725848024fb3ec6fdc8ca3f6b",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 6.2693877551020405,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 356
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "This isn't a drill. Amodei runs one of the most powerful AI labs on earth.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2cc9935ad0bc4b3e5c4b3e659a580359eae4ffb4863bdf5e49278b6083ccc295",
      "wav": "chunk-24.wav",
      "duration": 4.2260317460317465,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 373
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "When he says the role of developer changes \u2014 take it seriously, even if the timeline slips.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d435a6f901fb9b21b6af169f2adc5aea3e490da1769813df263766688132343d",
      "wav": "chunk-25.wav",
      "duration": 5.804988662131519,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 388
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "Will AI write all the code? Probably, eventually.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0aa2e07724d867f2cd7b9b1b261abc121ba4d04e22833eac945b6d16d25a259a",
      "wav": "chunk-26.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 405
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "text": "But the question that actually matters is: when it does, are you the person directing it \u2014 or the person it replaces?",
      "checksum": "sha256:2b35d19a14e7dc4f7085641e4c8ff94181eb74348e6438c10b6d95f6bfd94653",
      "wav": "chunk-27.wav",
      "duration": 6.780226757369615,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 413
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "text": "Let me know what you think in the comments.",
      "checksum": "sha256:51075db5b1134e31b9d9db56cb1ed0f7331ba5aab12e171530faa88a57edca8f",
      "wav": "chunk-28.wav",
      "duration": 2.089795918367347,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 435
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "text": "And if you want to learn more about AI, check out the dynamous.ai community.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9eba0717152126303daa8b39325181374b8adc8b596fd6d921008bd25f6218e7",
      "wav": "chunk-29.wav",
      "duration": 4.597551020408163,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 444
    }
  ]
}